    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] md:gap-16">
      <p class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-bone-300">
        The arc
      </p>
      <div>
        <h2
          class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-tighter text-bone-0"
          style="text-wrap: balance;"
        >
          The shape of the path is still being drawn.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-[60ch] text-[16px] leading-[1.65] text-bone-300">
          A working framework for how this changes over time — what AI takes
          on, what humans hold onto, and how the leverage moves. Coming back
          to this once the right phasing is clearer.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-bone-300">
          In progress
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

